1
00:00:00,600 --> 00:00:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">T-To the festival?!</font>

2
00:00:01,930 --> 00:00:04,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Wasshoi! Wasshoi! Wasshoi!</i></font>

3
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:06,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well... Yeah...</font>

4
00:00:07,730 --> 00:00:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always go with you guys, so I wanted 
to let you know ahead of time.</font>

5
00:00:12,510 --> 00:00:15,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, that's awesome. I'm so jealous!</font>

6
00:00:15,610 --> 00:00:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds nice, going to the summer 
festival with a guy.</font>

7
00:00:18,520 --> 00:00:20,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, then do you guys want to come with us?</font>

8
00:00:21,110 --> 00:00:23,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd feel better if you guys were there.</font>

9
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:24,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you an idiot?</font>

10
00:00:24,280 --> 00:00:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Read the room.</font>

11
00:00:25,420 --> 00:00:28,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I see, I see. That's right.</font>

12
00:00:28,390 --> 00:00:31,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The trial period is almost over,</font>

13
00:00:31,150 --> 00:00:34,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you guys would have to 
decide pretty soon, huh?</font>

14
00:00:39,770 --> 00:00:42,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what do you want
to do for the summer festival?</font>

15
00:00:42,370 --> 00:00:44,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's that time 
of the year, isn't it?</font>

16
00:00:45,570 --> 00:00:48,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The girls from Class D are all saying 
we should all go together, and—</font>

17
00:00:48,660 --> 00:00:49,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go.</font>

18
00:00:49,010 --> 00:00:49,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was fast.</font>

19
00:00:49,820 --> 00:00:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hey, Teach!</font>

20
00:00:52,090 --> 00:00:53,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Ichimura-kun?</font>

21
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:57,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going with Yoi-chan,
so can I be dismissed?</font>

22
00:00:57,990 --> 00:01:00,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?! That's the 
first I'm hearing of this!</font>

23
00:01:00,270 --> 00:01:01,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the first time I'm saying it.</font>

24
00:01:01,570 --> 00:01:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-When did you guys decide this?!</font>

25
00:01:03,140 --> 00:01:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yesterday.</font>

26
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yest—</font>

27
00:01:04,570 --> 00:01:07,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn you! Damn you to <i>hell</i>!</font>

28
00:01:07,050 --> 00:01:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit wishing ill on me.</font>

29
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:12,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hey, isn't your little 
experiment almost over?</font>

30
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:14,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You still don't have an answer?</font>

31
00:01:14,700 --> 00:01:16,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, there's no need to rush that.</font>

32
00:01:18,010 --> 00:01:19,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at you, getting carried away.</font>

33
00:01:19,570 --> 00:01:22,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you really okay saying that?</font>

34
00:01:22,780 --> 00:01:25,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She might just get taken 
by another man, y'know.</font>

35
00:01:25,870 --> 00:01:26,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

36
00:01:26,550 --> 00:01:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Prince has been looking 
oddly cute lately.</font>

37
00:01:29,670 --> 00:01:30,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true.</font>

38
00:01:30,710 --> 00:01:33,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's other guys who'd 
be interested in her, too, yeah?</font>

39
00:01:33,340 --> 00:01:36,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, if one of you falls 
in love with someone else,</font>

40
00:01:36,830 --> 00:01:38,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the contract gets terminated, right?</font>

41
00:01:38,990 --> 00:01:41,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shouldn't you be takin' it 
a little more seriously?</font>

42
00:01:41,910 --> 00:01:43,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just kiddin'!</font>

43
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:48,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder...</font>

44
00:01:49,140 --> 00:01:53,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whose mouth is that ridiculous 
claim coming from?</font>

45
00:01:51,290 --> 00:01:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}O-Ow, I'm sorry! I'm sorry!</font>

46
00:01:53,030 --> 00:01:56,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? It's <i>you</i>, Sentaro-kun!</font>

47
00:01:53,030 --> 00:01:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's the Romero Special!</font>

48
00:01:54,750 --> 00:01:57,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I said I was kiddin'!</font>

49
00:01:57,030 --> 00:01:58,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sentaro, you got this'?!</font>

50
00:01:58,190 --> 00:02:01,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}No, I give up! I give up!</font>

51
00:01:59,430 --> 00:02:00,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And, where's my sorry? Come on.</font>

52
00:02:00,170 --> 00:02:01,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}And the winner is Ichi!</font>

53
00:03:35,350 --> 00:03:37,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoi, Oji-kun.</font>

54
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Business is a bit slow right now, so I'm 
going to head out to get some things.</font>

55
00:03:40,550 --> 00:03:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two go ahead and eat.</font>

56
00:03:42,260 --> 00:03:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, okay.</font>

57
00:03:43,310 --> 00:03:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

58
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:48,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for the meal.</font>

59
00:03:50,930 --> 00:03:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, that's good!</font>

60
00:03:53,060 --> 00:03:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how many times I eat 
the curry here, it's delicious!</font>

61
00:03:56,290 --> 00:03:58,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dad would be happy to hear that.</font>

62
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:03,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, I partly took this
job for the free meals.</font>

63
00:04:03,050 --> 00:04:05,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Free meals are a perk, for sure.</font>

64
00:04:05,270 --> 00:04:07,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. Yoi-san, that drink you have...</font>

65
00:04:07,770 --> 00:04:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's a lassi.</font>

66
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:11,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A lassi?</font>

67
00:04:11,850 --> 00:04:13,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder if it's sweet.</i></font>

68
00:04:13,610 --> 00:04:15,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you like sweet things?</font>

69
00:04:15,450 --> 00:04:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no, not particularly—</font>

70
00:04:19,050 --> 00:04:21,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got a serious sweet tooth!</font>

71
00:04:21,580 --> 00:04:25,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't think I did, 
but apparently I do.</font>

72
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:27,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What do you mean, "apparently"?</font>

73
00:04:27,830 --> 00:04:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

74
00:04:29,770 --> 00:04:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, you're an interesting 
person, Yoi-san.</font>

75
00:04:36,380 --> 00:04:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

76
00:04:39,130 --> 00:04:43,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are yukatas... something guys like?</font>

77
00:04:44,940 --> 00:04:45,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

78
00:04:46,140 --> 00:04:51,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's just... my friend is planning to
go to the summer festival with a guy.</font>

79
00:04:52,650 --> 00:04:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems like she's having trouble 
deciding whether to wear one that day...</font>

80
00:04:57,170 --> 00:05:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... she's concerned 
about her boyish look</font>

81
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:04,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and whether it'd look good on her.</font>

82
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:07,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So she's wondering what to do.</font>

83
00:05:12,330 --> 00:05:15,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Regardless of whether
it looks good or not,</font>

84
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:17,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd say I definitely would be happy.</font>

85
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:18,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

86
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:23,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Knowing she went through all the trouble 
to dress up just for you</font>

87
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:25,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would make any guy excited.</font>

88
00:05:26,450 --> 00:05:28,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're surprisingly simple like that.</font>

89
00:05:29,690 --> 00:05:30,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, I see.</i></font>

90
00:05:31,940 --> 00:05:33,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

91
00:05:34,210 --> 00:05:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'll let her know that.</font>

92
00:05:36,510 --> 00:05:38,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad I could be of help.</font>

93
00:05:40,010 --> 00:05:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is that right.</i></font>

94
00:05:44,820 --> 00:05:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see.</i></font>

95
00:05:50,020 --> 00:05:50,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

96
00:05:52,330 --> 00:05:56,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you planning on going with someone 
to the summer festival, Yoi-san?</font>

97
00:05:57,450 --> 00:05:58,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What...</font>

98
00:06:05,070 --> 00:06:06,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm back!</font>

99
00:06:06,550 --> 00:06:08,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Welcome back!</font>

100
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you guys finished eating?</font>

101
00:06:10,570 --> 00:06:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it was delicious.</font>

102
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:16,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That took me by surprise...</i></font>

103
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Suddenly locking eyes with him when
he's so close is nerve-wrecking.</i></font>

104
00:06:19,690 --> 00:06:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's right.</font>

105
00:06:20,930 --> 00:06:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I picked up some customers on the way.</font>

106
00:06:23,450 --> 00:06:24,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

107
00:06:24,870 --> 00:06:28,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ta-da, it's Ichimura-kun and the gang!</font>

108
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey, it's really a curry place.</font>

109
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on in and have lots to eat!</font>

110
00:06:29,010 --> 00:06:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Curry! Curry!</font>

111
00:06:31,180 --> 00:06:32,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Senpai?!</i></font>

112
00:06:33,130 --> 00:06:34,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you...</font>

113
00:06:34,430 --> 00:06:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sentaro said he really wanted curry.</font>

114
00:06:39,910 --> 00:06:41,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Prince.</font>

115
00:06:41,510 --> 00:06:46,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was opposed to it 'cause I knew 
I'd get in trouble with you, but...</font>

116
00:06:47,910 --> 00:06:49,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

117
00:06:49,050 --> 00:06:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Did you always have this 
handsome guy working here?</font>

118
00:06:52,540 --> 00:06:53,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

119
00:06:53,220 --> 00:06:56,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey, please don't bother our part-timer.</font>

120
00:06:56,740 --> 00:06:59,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry about them.</font>

121
00:06:59,190 --> 00:07:00,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no worries.</font>

122
00:07:01,210 --> 00:07:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm, a new part-timer, huh?</font>

123
00:07:05,820 --> 00:07:07,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? What?</font>

124
00:07:07,470 --> 00:07:09,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a shame, Ichi.</font>

125
00:07:09,010 --> 00:07:10,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Such a fleeting love you had there.</font>

126
00:07:10,730 --> 00:07:13,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?! What're you guys talkin' about?</font>

127
00:07:21,810 --> 00:07:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Prince has been looking 
oddly cute lately.</i></font>

128
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:45,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's make sure I got your order right.</font>

129
00:07:45,730 --> 00:07:48,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A chicken, a beef, and a special, correct?</font>

130
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:51,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

131
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:53,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you staring 
at my face like that?</font>

132
00:07:53,770 --> 00:07:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? Oh, my bad, my bad.</font>

133
00:07:56,810 --> 00:07:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just thinkin' about how 
beautiful you are today.</font>

134
00:07:59,900 --> 00:08:00,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

135
00:08:03,450 --> 00:08:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey, Ichi, how do you say something 
so forward with such ease?</font>

136
00:08:08,290 --> 00:08:10,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come on. It's the truth, after all.</font>

137
00:08:10,110 --> 00:08:11,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey, he's making <i>me</i> blush.</font>

138
00:08:13,030 --> 00:08:15,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What is wrong with him?</i></font>

139
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:19,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Three new customers with 
one serving each, please.</font>

140
00:08:19,110 --> 00:08:20,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got it.</font>

141
00:08:20,450 --> 00:08:23,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Yoi-san, there's 
something on your ear.</font>

142
00:08:24,330 --> 00:08:25,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where is it?</font>

143
00:08:25,690 --> 00:08:27,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, a little to the left.</font>

144
00:08:27,620 --> 00:08:28,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

145
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:30,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, and a little down...</font>

146
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:33,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Right here.</font>

147
00:08:34,990 --> 00:08:35,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

148
00:08:36,870 --> 00:08:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What is that?</font>

149
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yogurt?</font>

150
00:08:41,820 --> 00:08:42,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

151
00:08:42,830 --> 00:08:44,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The lassi!</font>

152
00:08:45,290 --> 00:08:47,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's embarrassing.</font>

153
00:08:47,060 --> 00:08:48,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, not at all.</font>

154
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

155
00:08:51,890 --> 00:08:53,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oops, sorry.</font>

156
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seems like my hand slipped.</font>

157
00:08:55,770 --> 00:08:57,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ichi, you good?</font>

158
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no worries. 
We'll wipe it up right away.</font>

159
00:09:00,220 --> 00:09:01,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoi, get a rag.</font>

160
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

161
00:09:03,070 --> 00:09:04,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

162
00:09:04,860 --> 00:09:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, sorry about that.</font>

163
00:09:06,870 --> 00:09:08,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did it get on your clothes?</font>

164
00:09:08,590 --> 00:09:09,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah.</font>

165
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:11,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a good thing it didn't 
spill as much as I thought.</font>

166
00:09:12,150 --> 00:09:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep.</font>

167
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did it on purpose.</font>

168
00:09:19,420 --> 00:09:20,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

169
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:32,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Senpai, can we talk?</font>

170
00:09:32,590 --> 00:09:34,380
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#dcd0c8">Nasu Oyaji Curry</font></b></font></font></font>

171
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:36,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just what is going on here?</font>

172
00:09:36,420 --> 00:09:39,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could ban you from our store
for disruptive behavior, you know.</font>

173
00:09:39,270 --> 00:09:41,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm very sorry. I won't do it again.</font>

174
00:09:41,730 --> 00:09:43,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look me in the eye
when you say it, please.</font>

175
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez...</font>

176
00:09:45,300 --> 00:09:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That newbie <i>sure</i> is handsome, isn't he?</font>

177
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:56,820
