348
00:18:13,020 --> 00:18:14,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No... I'm fine.</font>

349
00:18:17,660 --> 00:18:18,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoops.</font>

350
00:18:20,060 --> 00:18:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

351
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:24,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay... Thank you very much.</font>

352
00:18:24,660 --> 00:18:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what are you doing here?</font>

353
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:29,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got business on the second-year floor?</font>

354
00:18:29,560 --> 00:18:31,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, um...</font>

355
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ichi!</font>

356
00:18:36,310 --> 00:18:37,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long's this gonna take?</font>

357
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:39,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ichi!</font>

358
00:18:39,320 --> 00:18:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm comin'!</font>

359
00:18:41,570 --> 00:18:42,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, Imma go.</font>

360
00:18:42,670 --> 00:18:44,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, um...</font>

361
00:18:47,450 --> 00:18:50,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to walk home together?</font>

362
00:18:55,090 --> 00:18:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me a sec.</font>

363
00:18:57,500 --> 00:18:59,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, guys, you go on ahead.</font>

364
00:18:59,270 --> 00:19:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? You sure?</font>

365
00:19:00,670 --> 00:19:01,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

366
00:19:01,950 --> 00:19:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See ya later!</font>

367
00:19:05,860 --> 00:19:06,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

368
00:19:15,220 --> 00:19:16,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go home.</font>

369
00:19:18,330 --> 00:19:20,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is there even anyone else...</i></font>

370
00:19:21,690 --> 00:19:24,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>who can make me feel this way?</i></font>

371
00:19:27,220 --> 00:19:30,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, did you need to do 
something in the staff room?</font>

372
00:19:30,790 --> 00:19:35,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, they found out I slipped out
 during lunch to buy a beef bowl.</font>

373
00:19:35,650 --> 00:19:38,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A beef... That'd definitely 
get you in trouble.</font>

374
00:19:38,600 --> 00:19:41,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really thought I wouldn't get caught.</font>

375
00:19:41,370 --> 00:19:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I used all sorts of secret shortcuts, too.</font>

376
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Come to think of it, he does come 
out of strange places, doesn't he?</i></font>

377
00:19:47,850 --> 00:19:50,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If only I were a wizard.</font>

378
00:19:50,280 --> 00:19:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could use a broom to zoom around, 
or become invisible to sneak out.</font>

379
00:19:54,540 --> 00:19:58,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wouldn't it be faster to use magic 
to make the beef bowl then?</font>

380
00:19:58,920 --> 00:20:00,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are a wizard, after all.</font>

381
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:02,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tou​ché.</font>

382
00:20:03,230 --> 00:20:04,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He didn't think of that?</i></font>

383
00:20:04,930 --> 00:20:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Genius! Marvelous! Beautiful!</font>

384
00:20:09,090 --> 00:20:11,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What does "beautiful" have 
to do with it?</i></font>

385
00:20:12,170 --> 00:20:15,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh... We're sort of having a 
normal conversation, aren't we?</i></font>

386
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:23,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, this is totally off the subject, 
but if you'd like, this is...</font>

387
00:20:23,030 --> 00:20:24,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who is even?!</i></font>

388
00:20:24,020 --> 00:20:24,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?!</font>

389
00:20:24,730 --> 00:20:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hello, Yoi-san? It's Oji.</i></font>

390
00:20:27,060 --> 00:20:28,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oji-kun?</font>

391
00:20:28,490 --> 00:20:31,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, I couldn't get 
a hold of the manager.</font>

392
00:20:31,630 --> 00:20:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you let him know that my train's 
delayed and I'm running a little late?</font>

393
00:20:35,460 --> 00:20:37,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, all right. Will do.</i></font>

394
00:20:37,540 --> 00:20:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

395
00:20:40,470 --> 00:20:43,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys exchanged numbers, huh?</font>

396
00:20:43,280 --> 00:20:46,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, yeah. We work in shifts, so...</font>

397
00:20:46,850 --> 00:20:48,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh...</font>

398
00:20:48,990 --> 00:20:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't like it.</font>

399
00:20:52,470 --> 00:20:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you know that Mr. Handsome 
clearly has a thing for you?</font>

400
00:20:57,440 --> 00:21:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? No, he doesn't.</font>

401
00:21:00,020 --> 00:21:01,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're just work buddies.</font>

402
00:21:02,610 --> 00:21:04,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess it's fine, if you don't see it.</font>

403
00:21:04,530 --> 00:21:09,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, you have a ton 
of numbers from girls, Senpai.</font>

404
00:21:10,030 --> 00:21:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll delete them all right now.</font>

405
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:13,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No, that's not the point!</font>

406
00:21:13,540 --> 00:21:15,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did it yesterday, too.</font>

407
00:21:15,610 --> 00:21:19,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you please lay off the talk 
about how jealous you are?</font>

408
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:25,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You might be used to 
saying that stuff to girls,</font>

409
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:28,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I have a hard time 
responding to it...</font>

410
00:21:29,160 --> 00:21:30,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not used to it.</font>

411
00:21:31,530 --> 00:21:33,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not used to stuff like this either!</font>

412
00:21:42,310 --> 00:21:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget it.</font>

413
00:21:43,900 --> 00:21:44,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Senpa—</font>

414
00:21:44,920 --> 00:21:45,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

415
00:21:46,050 --> 00:21:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Going home.</font>

416
00:21:54,660 --> 00:21:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, it's good to be cautious 
before you cross a stone bridge.</i></font>

417
00:21:57,720 --> 00:21:59,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But hitting it too many 
times may just break it.</i></font>

